rows.label: tlk45300157_02_msg0001
rows.name:
There was some kind of ruckus near
here during the night, you know?

rows.label: tlk45300157_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I was pretty scared this
place might be attacked.

rows.label: tlk45300157_02_msg0003
rows.name:
This facility is the most
important place in the city
after Hadashal Palace itself.

rows.label: tlk45300157_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If it were to go down,
basically all the city's
functions would become useless.

rows.label: tlk45300157_02_msg0005
rows.name: We have to keep a tight guard on it.
